text: The 2019 NFL season was the 100th season of the National Football League (NFL). The season ended with Kansas City Chiefs defeating the San Francisco 49ers in Super Bowl LIV at Hard Rock Stadium in Miami Gardens, Florida, on February 2, 2020. __TOC__ ==Regular season standings== ===Division=== ===Conference=== ==Postseason== ===Bracket===
